[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0055","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0055.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0410","title":"Sun Solaris cancel 命令本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中 cancel 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，该漏洞存在于 Solaris 7.0 及 Solaris 2.6 (i386) 版本中。本地攻击者可通过向 cancel 命令发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用该漏洞可获得 root 权限。由于攻击者需要本地系统访问权限，该漏洞的利用门槛较低，危害等级为高危（CVSS 7.2）。受影响的系统包括 Solaris 7.0 及更早版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0410"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.253","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 105401-01 (x86) 或 105400-01 (SPARC)，或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：移除 cancel 命令的 setuid root 权限 (chmod 755 /usr/bin/cancel)，或限制受信用户访问该命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/293","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19234","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0410.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0410","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0410.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0410.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r9mp-gf5j-985f/GHSA-r9mp-gf5j-985f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0410.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d0c16ada-3ed0-423a-99c8-dc346abdf212.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0055.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1025","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1025.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1256","title":"Oracle Database Assistant 数据库主密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Oracle Database Assistant 1.0（Oracle 8.0.3 Enterprise Edition 组件）在创建新数据库时，会将数据库主密码以明文形式写入 spoolmain.log 日志文件，导致本地攻击者可读取该日志文件获取管理员密码。该漏洞允许拥有本地系统访问权限的未授权用户窃取数据库凭证，进而可能获得数据库完全控制权限，危害数据机密性。需本地登录权限即可利用，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1256"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.053","remediation":"创建数据库后立即删除或限制 spoolmain.log 文件的访问权限，仅允许数据库管理员账户读取；同时升级到 Oracle 8i 或更高版本，新版本不再将明文密码写入日志文件。作为临时缓解措施，可配置数据库创建脚本在完成后自动清理 spoolmain.log 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92056752115116&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12744","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1902","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1256.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1256","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1256.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1256.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gfhx-4m9p-4j98/GHSA-gfhx-4m9p-4j98.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87815/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1256.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000564.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1025.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0054","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0054.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0409","title":"SuSE Linux gnuplot 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"S.u.S.E Linux 5.2 系统中 gnuplot 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于 gnuplot 在处理特定输入时未对数据长度进行充分检查，导致本地用户可通过向程序提交特制超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的关键数据，实现权限提升获取 root 权限。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限，无法远程利用。该漏洞影响 S.u.S.E Linux 5.2 等早期 Linux 发行版。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0409"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.127","remediation":"立即执行 `chmod -s /usr/bin/gnuplot` 移除 gnuplot 的 suid root 权限位，这是最直接有效的缓解措施。同时将 gnuplot 升级至 3.7 及以上版本，该版本已修复 plot.c 中 HOME 环境变量的栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。如使用 S.u.S.E 系统，可将 `/etc/rc.config` 中 `PERMISSION_SECURITY` 设为 `\"paranoid\"` 以自动管理 suid 权限。作为深度防御，建议限制普通用户对 svgalib 和 /dev/mem 的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/319","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19254","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0409.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0409","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0409.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0409.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g722-hhhg-4rh7/GHSA-g722-hhhg-4rh7.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0409.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0054.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1179","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1179.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1551","title":"Ipswitch IMail 5.0/6.0 Web服务 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ipswitch IMail 邮件服务器的 Web 服务（5.0 及 6.0 版本）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。其 Web 服务在处理用户请求的 URL 时未对输入长度进行边界校验，当攻击者向目标服务器发送超长 URL 时，会触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃并造成拒绝服务（DoS）。在特定条件下，攻击者还可能进一步利用该溢出执行任意命令。该漏洞影响运行 Ipswitch IMail 5.0/6.0 Web 服务的系统，攻击条件为攻击者能够与目标 Web 服务端口建立网络连接并发送特制 HTTP 请求，无需身份认证的远程攻击者即可发起攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1551"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:41.970","remediation":"升级到最新的 Ipswitch IMail 版本以获取安全补丁，如无法立即更新可禁用 Web 服务端口以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92038879607336&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/505","https://