版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1046"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.570","remediation":"建议立即将 Ipswitch IMail 升级至 6.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复 IMonitor 在 8181 端口的缓冲区溢出问题。如暂时无法升级，应在防火墙/边界设备上封锁对 TCP 8181 端口的外部访问，仅允许可信管理网段连接，并停用非必需的 IMonitor 服务，同时启用连接速率限制以降低拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92038879607336&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/504","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1897","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19379","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5462f02b07d84a047e686909ca72147a67d01e8a/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1046.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1046","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1046.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/86aad396c74c8e8e5de3bdfcc6d28d9cc5001c7e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1046.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6da213119b3c54637329347c0dc42c66b8a84f0a/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xfpj-rg74-76g7/GHSA-xfpj-rg74-76g7.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/imail_imonitor_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1046.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000561.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--13b95207-f3e9-46d0-8371-a29972cbc481.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1685.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0151","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0151.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0479","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server HP-UX VirtualVault 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 在 HP-UX VirtualVault 平台上存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制请求，触发服务进程异常崩溃，导致正常用户无法访问 Web 服务。该漏洞影响运行于 HP-UX VVOS 系统上的 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。目前厂商已停止支持该产品，建议用户迁移至其他受支持的 Web 服务器软件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0479"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.133","remediation":"安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9903-092 中提供的补丁程序。由于 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 及 HP-UX VirtualVault VVOS 均已停止技术支持，建议迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器平台（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx）及现代操作系统。如无法立即迁移，可在网络边界防火墙配置访问控制规则，仅允许可信 IP 访问服务端口（默认 80/443），并限制对服务端口的异常请求频率以缓解 DoS 攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9903-092"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0151.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0144","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0144.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0476","title":"SCO TermVision 口令弱加密算法漏洞","description":"SCO TermVision 使用弱加密算法存储用户密码，本地攻击者无需身份认证即可逆向解密获取明文凭据，进而获得系统未授权访问权限。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 系统，攻击者需具有本地访问权限，利用门槛较低。厂商已发布安全更新修复此加密缺陷。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0476"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.750","remediation":"SCO TermVision 已停止维护多年，SCO 公司已不再运营，官方无补丁可用。根本修复措施：迁移至受支持的终端仿真方案（如 OpenSSH + 现代终端客户端），并停用 TermVision 服务。临时缓解措施：（1）限制本地用户登录权限，仅授权可信用户使用系统；（2）使用 `chmod 600` 加固密码文件权限，启用 shadow password 机制；（3）部署主机入侵检测系统监控异常密码解密行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0476"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0144.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0114","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0114.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0440","title":"Netscape Communicator Java Virtual Machine 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Java虚拟机（JVM）中的字节码验证器组件存在安全缺陷，攻击者可将精心构造的恶意Java小程序（Applet）嵌入网页中。当用户使用Netscape Communicator或Navigator浏览器访问该恶意页面时，字节码验证器未能正确检测恶意字节码，导致攻击者能够在受害者系统上远程执行任意代码。该漏洞影响Netscape Communicator 4.x及更早版本，CVSS评分7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0440"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.073","remediation":"立即升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.5 以上版本，或安装 Sun 于 1999 年 3 月发布的 JVM 安全补丁。在浏览器设置中禁用 Java applet 自动执行功能，并将安全级别调至最高。鉴于该产品已停止维护，建议彻底停止使用 Netscape Communicator/Navigator，迁移至现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://java.sun.com/pr/1999/03/pr990329-01.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92333596624452&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1939","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0440.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0440","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0440.md","https://github.com/anchore/nvd-data-overrides/blob/36d2cee8de6aec9cb5b26c2fc42ccdfc645e43b2/data/1999/CVE-1999-0440.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wwvm-jq77-pvrq/GHSA-wwvm-jq77-pvrq.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/9e2c01529685dbbb213203143ecd2246f53ad9e5/1999/CVE-1999-0440.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0114.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0109","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0109.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0437","title":"Ramp Networks WebRamp Router HTTP Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ramp Networks WebRamp 路由器 HTTP 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需任何身份认证，仅通过网络向目标设备80端口的HTTP服务发送特制的恶意字符串，即可触发该漏洞，导致路由器HTTP服务崩溃或停止响应正常请求。攻击条件极为简单，只需目标WebRamp设备的HTTP端口处于开放状态即可，CVSS评分5.0，危害等级中等。建议用户升级固件或通过防火墙规则限制对HTTP端口的非必要网络访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0437"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.680","remediation":"建议在防火墙或访问控制列表(ACL)中限制对 WebRamp 路由器 HTTP 端口(80/tcp)的访问，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 地址。如设备 Web 管理非必需，直接关闭 HTTP 服务。由于该产品已停产且厂商不再提供更新，长期方案为替换为仍在安全支持周期内的现代路由器产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0437","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0437.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0437","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0437.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0437.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r2qf-rrg7-5x8j/GHSA-r2qf-rrg7-5x8j.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0437.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82815/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000557.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f5743b00-53ea-4384-b905-75b5901b7e63.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0109.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0108","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0436","title":"HP HP-UX Domain Enterprise Server Management System 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 Domain Enterprise Server Management System (DESMS) 存在权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者利用 DESMS 组件在权限管理上的缺陷，可将其权限提升至 root 级别，进而完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，需本地系统访问权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议用户应用 HP 官方安全补丁以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0436"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.550","remediation":"安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9903-095 对应的 DESMS 补丁包（如 PHSS_* 系列补丁）。如无需 DESMS 功能，可移除或停止相关服务（/sbin/init.d/desms stop；rm /sbin/init.d/desms）。限制本地控制台访问权限，仅允许受信管理员登录。建议升级至受支持的 HP-UX 版本（11i v3 以上），其默认不包含 DESMS 组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9903-095"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0108.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0107","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0107.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0435","title":"HP HP-UX MC/ServiceGuard 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统的 MC/ServiceGuard 与 MC/LockManager 组件存在权限管理缺陷，本地用户通过 SAM 工具可利用该漏洞获取系统高级权限，实现权限提升。攻击者需具有目标系统的本地账号才能发起攻击，成功利用后可完全控制受影响的 HP-UX 系统，导致机密性、完整性和可用性丧失。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0435"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.417","remediation":"建议立即安装 HP 针对 MC/ServiceGuard 和 MC/LockManager 发布的安全补丁（HP-UX 11.00 及更早版本对应的 PHSS 补丁包），将 MC/ServiceGuard 和 MC/LockManager 升级至修复后的版本。如无法立即打补丁，可在 /etc/PATH 中限制普通用户对 SAM 命令的访问权限，移除 /usr/sbin/sam 等二进制文件的 setuid 位，并通过 SAM 授权配置文件限制仅允许受信任管理员用户使用该工具。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0435"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0107.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0097","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0097.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0432","title":"HP HP-UX FTP 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 11.00 操作系统的 FTP 服务存在权限提升漏洞，本地用户可利用该漏洞获取更高系统权限。由于 FTP 程序对用户权限校验不严格，已获得本地账户的攻击者登录系统后，可通过 FTP 工具的权限缺陷突破访问限制，获取非授权的文件读取或操作权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 11.00 版本，CVSS v2 评分 4.6，危害等级中等，攻击复杂度低。HP 已发布安全公告 HPSBUX9903-094 并提供修复方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0432"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.010","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9903-094 提供的对应补丁包（HP-UX 11.00 ftp 权限提升补丁）。如无法立即修补，可临时移除 /usr/bin/ftp 文件的 SUID 权限：执行 chmod 555 /usr/bin/ftp 阻止非授权用户以特权身份执行 ftp 命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9903-094"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0097.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0087","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0087.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0430","title":"Cisco Catalyst系列LAN交换机远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco Catalyst 系列局域网交换机（包括 Catalyst 2900/1200/5000 系列）的管理员模块软件存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送特制的网络数据包，强制目标交换机上的管理模块（Supervisor Module）重新加载，导致交换机暂时停止转发网络流量，造成拒绝服务。攻击者只需具备网络连通性即可利用此漏洞，无需任何权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0430"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.743","remediation":"升级 Catalyst 5000 系列交换机 Supervisor 软件至 5.4(1) 或更新版本以修复远程触发 Supervisor 模块重载的拒绝服务漏洞。该系列产品已停止技术支持，建议迁移至当前仍受支持的 Cisco Catalyst 9000 系列交换机以获得持续安全更新。若暂时无法替换设备，可在网络入口 ACL 中限制对 Catalyst 交换机管理接口（SNMP/Telnet/HTTP）的访问来源 IP，仅允许受信任的管理网段连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1103","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0430.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0430","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0430.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0430.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/513.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r4m8-cpvh-q29r/GHSA-r4m8-cpvh-q29r.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/rm-hull/linux-journal-archive/blob/4a2e1e18d27174397e3dff73ae07d78c0d3c3719/LJ/listings/102/6222l2.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/C/cisco_dos.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0087.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0086","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0086.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0429","title":"Lotus Notes 客户端加密邮件明文传输信息泄露漏洞","description":"Lotus Notes 4.5 客户端存在加密邮件明文传输漏洞。当用户发送加密邮件但未设置\"Encrypt Saved Mail\"首选项时，客户端会将加密邮件的副本以明文形式在网络上传输，导致加密保护失效。远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探方式捕获并读取本应加密的邮件内容，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Lotus Notes 4.5 及可能的相关版本，攻击条件简单，只需攻击者处于同一网络段。官方建议用户启用\"Encrypt Saved Mail\"首选项以缓解风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0429"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.620","remediation":"在 Lotus Notes 4.5 客户端中，依次进入\"文件→偏好设置→邮件\"，勾选\"Encrypt Saved Mail\"选项以强制加密已保存邮件。建议升级至 Lotus Notes 5.0 或更高版本，新版默认启用此安全选项。如无法升级，可在邮件服务器和客户端之间启用 SSL/TLS 加密传输作为额外缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92221437025743&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92241547418689&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92246997917866&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92249282302994&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0429.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0429","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0429.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0429.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-364x-96mf-p447/GHSA-364x-96mf-p447.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0429.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000554.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b240f787-e786-4698-8910-dd2f7ddf7c71.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0086.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0079","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0079.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0426","title":"Linux Kernel /dev/kmem 默认权限不当导致 IP 欺骗漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.0.36 之前版本中 /dev/kmem 设备文件的默认权限设置不当，导致本地普通用户可读取内核内存空间。攻击者利用该漏洞可获取内核中的 TCP 序列号等敏感信息，进而实施盲 TCP 欺骗攻击，伪造 TCP 连接或破坏现有连接，影响系统通信安全。该漏洞无需特殊攻击条件，拥有本地账户即可利用，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0426"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.267","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.36 及以上版本，该版本修复了 /dev/kmem 默认权限问题。如无法升级内核，可将 /dev/kmem 权限修改为 640 或更严格，仅允许 root 用户读取，以降低 IP 欺骗攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0426","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19458","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0426.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0426.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0426","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0426.json","https://github.com/bb1nfosec/Information-Security-Tasks/blob/14e2094f7bd96d2cb82493a9a6968ae7aa4fed5e/feeds/2026-06-07.md","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0426.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vgr8-rhcx-42jv/GHSA-vgr8-rhcx-42jv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0426.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82490/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0079.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0079.toml"}]